called Arunachal Pradesh as part of China.

209
00:09:10,190 --> 00:09:14,440
Now, it’s possible someone might have corrected
this obvious blunder

210
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,950
before it ever aired,

211
00:09:15,950 --> 00:09:20,269
but then again ESPN did tell employees not
to discuss China,

212
00:09:20,269 --> 00:09:23,040
Hong Kong politics in an internal memo.

213
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:25,790
And now you know why I’ve spent seven years
of my life

214
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:27,339
making a show warning Americans

215
00:09:27,339 --> 00:09:29,760
about the Chinese Communist Party.

216
